<view class="page"><view class="hero-card"><view class="hero-title">花园成长规则</view><view class="hero-subtitle">照料越用心，花朵成长越快</view></view><view class="card"><view class="section-title">动作得分</view><view class="score-grid"><view class="score-item"><view class="score-icon">💧</view><view class="score-name">浇水</view><view class="score-value">+1~3</view></view><view class="score-item"><view class="score-icon">🧪</view><view class="score-name">施肥</view><view class="score-value">+2~4</view></view><view class="score-item"><view class="score-icon">🌿</view><view class="score-name">除草</view><view class="score-value">+1~2</view></view><view class="score-item"><view class="score-icon">✂️</view><view class="score-name">修剪</view><view class="score-value">+1</view></view><view class="score-item"><view class="score-icon">📤</view><view class="score-name">分享好友</view><view class="score-value">+2</view></view></view><view class="highlight">不同花种的每次成长值不同，以上为当前配置范围。</view></view><view class="card"><view class="section-title">阶段成长</view><view class="timeline"><view class="timeline-row"><view class="dot"></view><view class="line"></view><view class="dot"></view><view class="line"></view><view class="dot"></view></view><view class="timeline-labels"><view class="timeline-label">种子 (seed)</view><view class="timeline-label">幼苗 (sprout)</view><view class="timeline-label">盛放 (bloom)</view></view></view><view class="highlight">阶段阈值由花种配置决定：幼苗通常 9~18 分，盛放通常 18~35 分。</view></view><view class="card"><view class="section-title">详细说明</view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">1.</text><text class="rule-text">每位用户初次进入会初始化花园，花种在种子商店按等级逐步解锁。</text></view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">2.</text><text class="rule-text">浇水、施肥、除草、修剪每天各 1 次（按每株花单独统计），达到上限后当日不可重复操作。</text></view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">3.</text><text class="rule-text">护理行为会同步影响水分、肥力、健康，并为该花增加成长值；同时累计到你的总积分。</text></view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">4.</text><text class="rule-text">等级由总积分决定（Lv1~Lv8），当前阈值为 0/80/180/320/520/800/1180/1680。</text></view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">5.</text><text class="rule-text">在护理页点击“分享给朋友”，每次成功分享可获得 2 积分（按每株花每日限制）。</text></view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">6.</text><text class="rule-text">排行榜按总积分排名，护理记录可在“我的记录”中查看。</text></view></view><view class="tip-card">小提示：高等级花种通常成长收益更高，但每日动作次数仍按规则限制。</view></view>